snippet.title: Street Fighter Alpha 3 Trailer 2002
snippet.description:
Street Fighter Alpha 3 Trailer 2002

Official Content From Capcom

The alumni of SF 2 are joined by 4 new characters plus 4 hidden characters. The graphical prowess and arcade-perfect gameplay make this the latest standard in 2D fighters.
Platforms: Sega Dreamcast, Sony PlayStation, Gameboy Advanced
